title: The Water Horse Legend of the Deep.ISO  NTSC  DVD5
description:
Angus, a young boy living in WWII Scotland, has grown more and more declusive 

since his father wend off to war. During a solitary search for sea shells on the 

beach, a pastime he shared with his father, Angus finds a mysterious object on the
 
shore. Uncertain of its origin, he takes it home, hiding it for safe keeping. 

However, when it hatches overnight, he finds himself the proud but puzzled 

caretaker of a waterhorse - a sea creature of mythic proportions.




Format: ISO

Region: 1,   NTSC
